Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Gets Angry!\NA Dirty Trick Violates The Sacred Duel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He blocked the blow with his helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was off by even an inch,\Nhe would've died instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of their attacks is a mortal blow\Naimed at the opponent's vital point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have continued this\Nduel to the death for 100 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is good... We can use this\Nopportunity to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without a reason,\Nthey're fighting so seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fight sure is a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:04:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what people mean\Nby a real battle between men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To use an analogy, those two fly\Na warrior's flag in their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This flag is even more\Nimportant than their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In no way do they want it\Nto be destroyed by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they've continued to take\Non each other for 100 long years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it? This is unmistakably
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a "proud duel" between "warriors"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever... Stuff like that\Ndoesn't interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna watch this a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly what my goal is...\NTo be a "brave warrior of the sea"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be a proud man like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So you wanna be a giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!! Were you even listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Don't you have\Nto watch them over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a village with\Nwarriors like them in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go there someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a good view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find you, Miss Valentine.\NCome down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mr. 5... After all,\Nthey're absorbed in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you really get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big job for 200 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I feel reluctant\Nto do as Mr. 3 tells us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both getting homesick,\Naren't we, Dorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll beat you\Nand go back to Elbaf, Broggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,73,466 duels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,73,466 draws...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorry! Actually,\NI got alcohol from my guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! It's been a while since\NI had a drink. Give me some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First a long, strange earthquake,\Nand now this? What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there weird creatures other\Nthan dinosaurs in this jungle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that damn cook is\Nprobably the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who'd be happy to\Ncapture things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were those bird cries?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, those were vulgar,\Nunappetizing cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we're competing to capture a\Nbig prey, we're still looking for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does it have to be big,\Nit also has to be tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy doesn't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. His guests are your friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a man with a long nose and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Usopp and Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! They said they\Nwouldn't get off the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they really do like\Nadventures after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could also say that\NI got this alcohol from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Dorry-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,does it really take a year\Nfor the Log to be stored?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice the\Nhuman skulls lying around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who come to this island die\Nbefore the Log is stored in most cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some become dinosaurs' food.\NSome suffer from the heat and starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some others are killed because\Nthey attack us. They all die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that one year on this\Nisland is too long for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?\NEven if we could survive for a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if that much time passes, I don't know\Nwhat will happen to my country by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'd get bored, too,\Nif we stay here for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a good way, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do have an Eternal Pose,\Nbut it's to our hometown, Elbaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we're fighting\Nfor this Eternal Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna try taking it by force?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.\NThat's not where we wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanna go to the island\Nafter this one. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose the route to Alabasta,\Nthere's no point in moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you\Nmove forward randomly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're lucky, you'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may actually get there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there was someone\Nwho left before the Log was stored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've gotten to the next island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand what they're thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brave warrior of the sea? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about you guys.\NI wanna be like you guys someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? You mean a giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See?\N--That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to live proudly\Njust like the warriors of Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since our life span\Nis longer than you humans',
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we think about how we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your assets, life...\NEverything will eventually cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we could die as a warrior of\NElbaf without destroying our pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that would be "dying with honor."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pride is an everlasting treasure\Nthat is passed on in the land of Elbaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So pride is your treasure...\NThat's so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just decided... that I'll\Ncall you Master from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the alcohol explode?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the alcohol\Nwe had on our ship, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It exploded in his stomach!\NHis opponent must've laid the explosive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you watching?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been fighting for 100 years!\NNo way they'd do something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Broggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're proud warriors of Elbaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else besides you\Nshould I be suspicious of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here for now! It's\Nprobably no use saying anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably no use even if we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this and stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me! Are you going to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad to do this to the old guy,\Nbut I'll quiet him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorry-san, please listen!\NWe really don't know anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything about the alcohol that exploded!\NSo please don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to stay calm!\NYour insides are in bad shape right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...\Ndo something so insolent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:16:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he has... the powers of a Devil Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is actually good.\NOtherwise he wouldn't have calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the old guy said, this alcohol\Nexplosion isn't the act of the other giant,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my friends would never\Ndo a stupid thing like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone else...\Non this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Games are heavily influenced\Nby people's state of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are confused right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by the cryptic bomb service\Nfrom an invisible enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, about our first target,\NDorry the Blue Ogre...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was impossible to finish him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the damage he received in his\Nstomach still must've been quite large.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can drink some tea and\Nwait for the next duel to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll let the other giant take\Ncare of the injured giant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a roundabout\Nway of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warrior species is the\Nsame as wild boars, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to fight seriously when\Nthey're only good at going head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since even if we can't win power-wise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have brains that can make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Get it yourself, Miss Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what're we going\Nto do with the Straw Hat gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat? Oh yeah, the small fries\Nthat found out the Boss's secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can just lure them out one by\None starting with whoever's convenient
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to my "service set"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My motto is "big crimes via cheap tricks."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're many ways to defeat\Nenemies without actually fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3, refill please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Take time to savor it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mountain is...\Nif I'm not mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.\NI'm running out of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Let it go! I said sorry! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to\Nmess around! Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time-out signal has rung.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having no prey isn't even funny... Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite active today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going?! Your wounds from\Nthat last battle still haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!\NWe're both in the same condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making excuses during a merciless\Nfight to the death would spoil my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go, Dorry-san!\NYou need to keep still!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Warrior Dorry, am here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will fight to uphold the name of Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gentle song
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it there for us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a wave washed away\Nthat little sand castle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked up at the passing\Nclouds with a sad smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find the world is full of enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold you in my arms forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami has disappeared!\NWhat am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel that's been interfered\Nwith isn't a duel anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?! Who's doing this?!\NShow yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you violate the proud battle?!\NYou won't get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Broggy's Bitter Tears Of Victory!\NThe Conclusion Of Elbaf"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
